WHAT is Django 5?

Django is a high-level web framework written in python that encourages rapid development and 
clean, pragmatic design.
 
Django emphasizes reusabilty and don't repeat yourself(DRY) principal , which means it tries to keep your code simple and not repititive,

It follows the Model View Template (MVT) architectural pattern .

It was created on 2003 at Lawrence Journal World Newspaper.

It wasreleased publicly under a BSD license in july 2005.

In june 2008, it was announced that Django Software Foundation would maintiain DJANGO IN FUTURE.

Features and Advantages of Django5?
=>
Built in Admin Interface
ORM
Authentication System
Rapid Development
Versatility
Security

